docs.summary:
Possible values are:
  • UNKNOWN
  • ADD_REMOVE_ELEMENTS
  • CHANGE_ICON
  • CHANGE_COMPANY_NAME

Possible values are:
  • DRAFT - draft logo
  • PURCHASED - purchased logo
  • PENDING_TOUCH_UP - logo being touched up
  • UNKNOWN - a mistake that we now need to keep because it's written in the db
  • PURCHASED_DRAFT - draft generated from a purchased logo

Possible values are:
  • PENDING_PAYMENT
  • PAYMENT_APPROVED
  • PENDING_UPLOADS
  • PENDING_ARCHIVE
  • COMPLETE
  • COMPLETE_TOUCH_UP
  • COMPLETE_UNLIMITED
  • CANCELLED
  • FAILED

Possible values are:
  • PNG
  • JPEG

Possible values are:
  • PERCENT
  • PIXELS

Possible values are:
  • NONE
  • HORIZONTAL
  • VERTICAL
  • BOTH

Possible values are:
  • NONE
  • NOUN_PROJECT
  • PAID_NOUN_PROJECT
  • WIX
  • WIX_CMS
  • LOGO_CMS_NOUN
  • LOGO_CMS_WIX
  • NEW_WIX_CMS

Possible values are:
  • LEFT
  • CENTER
  • RIGHT

  • RECTANGLE
  • TRIANGLE
  • CIRCLE

Possible values are:
  • DEFAULT - Default behavior is to take each first letter of each word, capitalize and concatinate them.

Possible values are:

Possible values are:
  • NONE - Default case - no change in casing
  • UPPER_CASE - Upper case all letters
  • LOWER_CASE - Lower case all letters
  • TITLE_CASE - Camelcase lettering
